parameters:
\SE[31] Excuse me. I have brought two individuals who wish to
have an interview with you, Master. \SE[0]

\SE[2]These are Vega-sama and Cat-sama. They seem to have
requested an interview through Koudain's services. \SE[1]Well
then, I will return to my regular duties.

Wait, don't leave. I have assigned you today's special task. Stay
there and wait.

Well then, let's begin the interview. You can learn about the job
from your seniors. Today, I just want to see your determination.

Hmm. If you have accumulated dedication in your daily life... I
believe that failures in work are trivial matters.

Such things depend on an individual's essence. I want to feel
even a little bit of that.

\SE[50]I see... I understand it well now. \!\SE[3]Thank you very
much.

\SE[51] (Even though you've risen through corruption, you have
quite an impressive code of conduct for someone so arrogant.)

Well then, from you. What kind of things can you do here to be of
use to me?

\SE\SE[45]I have had experience in a similar line of work before.
I believe I can meet your expectations without fail.
\SE[45]...And also.

\SE[46] (If it is what Master desires... \!\SE[47]I believe I can
fulfill any requests you have, \!\SE[45]in any way you
desire...)
You... That's great! Yes! It's a hiring...!!
So, what will you do for me...?
\SE[67] (Oh no... I completely skipped my lines due to shock...)

Ohh... Such innocent shyness...! You're quite good too! You're in
my strike zone...!

Then try saying this line! If you can say it well, I'll also hire
you!

I may not be perfect, but I will wholeheartedly do my best to
satisfy you, my master. ...Yes!

Mmm... I wonder if it's too embarrassing to say...? But I really
want to hear it in your cute voice, you know...?

\SE[92] (This person...! \!\SE[67]Guh...\. But if I just say it,
it's hired....)

(Melissa and the others also want to meet Nikita... What's the
big deal about a little embarrassment!)

\SE[66]I-I may not be perfect.... B-but... I will do my best...
with all my heart and soul... to satisfy you, my master....

Hired... It's hired!! \!It's still rough, but I have high hopes
for your potential...! Please continue to do your best in the
future...!

Hehehe... I'm looking forward to our special assignment
together... Are you excited too...?
\SE[75] (If it comes to that, I'll kill you.)

Shall we start the training right away? If you're okay with it,
it would be good for you to receive guidance on the duties from
the senior maids.
\SE\SE[0]Yes, gladly. \!\SE[0]I will do as you wish.
\SE[4]I have no problem with it either.

Yeah, it's good that you're motivated. \!Then wait for me in the
break room. I'll ask someone to assign you tasks.
\SE\SE[0]Understood. \SE[0]Then, I will take my leave here.
Nfufu~.... I've picked up some good kids~.

Hey, it's a special assignment. Today... Yeah, let's do the usual
thing. Make it like the day you were first sold.
